<%# app/views/booking_mailer/confirmation.text.erb %>
Booking Confirmed — The Anchorpoint Retreat
=============================================

Dear <%= @booking.guest_name %>,

Thank you for booking your stay at The Anchorpoint Retreat. Your reservation is confirmed!

Confirmation Number: <%= @booking.confirmation_number %>

STAY DETAILS
------------
Property:   <%= @property.name %>
Check-in:   <%= @booking.check_in.strftime("%A, %B %d, %Y") %>
Check-out:  <%= @booking.check_out.strftime("%A, %B %d, %Y") %>
Nights:     <%= @booking.num_nights %>
Guests:     <%= @booking.num_guests %>

PAYMENT SUMMARY
---------------
Amount Paid: <%= @amount_paid %>
<% if @balance_due -%>
Balance Due: <%= @balance_due %>

Your remaining balance will be due before check-in.
<% end -%>

GETTING THERE
-------------
Address: <%= @property.address %>, <%= @property.city %>, <%= @property.state %> <%= @property.zip %>
Check-in:  <%= @property.check_in_time %>
Check-out: <%= @property.check_out_time %>

If you have any questions before your stay, don't hesitate to reach out.

Warm regards,
The Anchorpoint Retreat Team

---
This email was sent to <%= @booking.guest_email %>.
